<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  animated fadeIn" style="opacity:1;-webkit-animation-delay:0.5s;-webkit-animation-duration:1s;-webkit-animation-iteration-count:1; -moz-animation-delay:0.5s;-moz-animation-duration:1s;-moz-animation-iteration-count:1; animation-delay:0.5s;animation-duration:1s;animation-iteration-count:1;test">
<div class="wpb_wrapper">
<p><strong><a class="noline" href="mailto:jsears@rivpartners.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jason Sears<br>
</a></strong><em><span style="color: #808080;">Executive Vice President</span></em><strong><a class="noline" href="mailto:jsears@rivpartners.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><br>
</a></strong></p>
<p>Prior to joining Rivington Partners, Jason was an Executive Vice President at Dual Commercial, a Managing General Agency with $200M in annual gross written premium.</p>
<p>Jason has&nbsp;worked in numerous capacities and areas&nbsp;of the insurance marketplace in his career, including carriers (QBE, ASI), underwriting (AIG), reinsurance brokerage (B&amp;W Re) and captive / reinsurance structures (Commonwealth Risk Services).</p>
<p>Jason&nbsp;graduated from Swarthmore College with a B.A. in History and played Varsity Soccer.</p>
