</a></strong></p>
<p>Sunil is responsible for managing financial and operational aspects for the Rivington Partners.&nbsp; Prior to joining Rivington Partners, Sunil was an Associate at Southport Lane, a private equity firm focused on the insurance and financial services industries, responsible for underwriting insurance transactions to maximize risk-adjusted returns.&nbsp; He spent three years at Bank of America Merrill Lynch as an Associate, helping to build the investment bank’s underwriting and ratings &amp; risk analysis platform for investing in distributed solar projects.</p>
<p>Sunil is a Carnegie Mellon University graduate with a degree in Finance and Statistics.</p>
