<div class="wpb_wrapper">
<p><strong><a class="noline" href="mailto:rchristofer@rivpartners.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rick Christofer<br>
</a></strong><span style="color: #808080;"><em>Chief Underwriting Officer</em></span><strong><a class="noline" href="mailto:rchristofer@rivpartners.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><br>
</a></strong></p>
<p>Rick oversees all aspects of Rivington’s underwriting function. His responsibilities encompass strategy, production, product development and management, and P&amp;L performance.</p>
<p>Rick has over 20 years’ experience in insurance and reinsurance underwriting &amp; brokerage. Prior to joining Rivington Partners, he was Specialty Product Executive at AIG, Treaty Reinsurance Broker at Guy Carpenter, Casualty Underwriter at Gen Re &amp; Commercial Underwriter at The Hartford Insurance Co.</p>
<p>Rick graduated from Notre Dame where he played Varsity Soccer.</p>
